      "body": "Request for clarification: for mempool transactions that did not signal RBT through their sequence (`IsRBFOptIn()` returns `RBFTransactionState::FINAL`) the `getmempoolentry` RPC returned `bip125-replaceable=false`, but the behavior was replaceable. With this change the `bip125-replaceable` field is not returned, and the replaceable behavior is unchanged.\n\n",
